Name: RSS Feed widget

Author: Jeff Madsen (www.codebyjeff.com)

Date: 2012-01-10

Version: 1.0

This widget allow you to create a simple rss feed and configure the number of posts you'd like to display.

In the main application/views/home/index.php, add:

<section class="small" data-site="The Onion" data-url="http://feeds.theonion.com/theonion/daily" data-feedcount="5" data-widget="rss"></section>


